Overview

Anna requires GNU make and GCC to build. Anna also depends on the
following external libraries:

* Flex
* Bison
* GNU MP

Anna should build and run on any modern 32 or 64 bit UNIX-like system
with the above dependencies met. For OS specific installation
instructions, read on below.

Installing on Debian-like systems, including Ubuntu

sudo apt-get install gcc bison flex libgmp3-dev make
make -s && sudo make install

